<p>Howdy <%= @resource.email %>!</p>

<p>A request has been made to change your password. You can verify this via the following link.</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) %></p>

<p>If this is not your request, please ignore.</p>
<p>Your password will not be altered until the link has been accessed and changes have been committed.</p>
